法识别到--mount 这个选项命令。</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://gitee.com/wovvvv/tumo/raw/master/1668224697412-2022-11-1211:44:58.png\"/></p>\n<h2>这个是我的系统版本</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://gitee.com/wovvvv/tumo/raw/master/1668224726574-2022-11-1211:45:27.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://gitee.com/wovvvv/tumo/raw/master/1668224801783-2022-11-1211:46:42.png\"/></p>\n<h2>这个是我的 wsl2 内核版本</h2>\n","last_modified":1668224844,"replies":12,"id":894670},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7f8/a7fb/716_large.png?m=1651385997","name":"docker","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7f8/a7fb/716_normal.png?m=1651385997","title":"Docker","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/docker","topics":1036,"footer":"","header":"基于 Linux Container 技术的轻量级虚拟化环境。","title_alternative":"Docker","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7f8/a7fb/716_mini.png?m=1651385997","stars":1267,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":716,"parent_node_name":"cloud"},"member":{"id":561247,"username":"wapollo9","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wapollo9","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ea16cfab62d775b1c782b0074cc141b7?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ea16cfab62d775b1c782b0074cc141b7?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ea16cfab62d775b1c782b0074cc141b7?s=73&d=retro","created":1636427220,"last_modified":1636427220},"last_reply_by":"cpstar","last_touched":1668235729,"title":"Docker 能否直通网卡","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894659","created":1668221327,"deleted":0,"content":"想用 Docker 跑 OpenWrt 做主路由，配置网卡后发现 wlan 网卡被映射成了 eth 网卡，OpenWrt 好像无法通过映射之后的 eth 网卡开热点，请问怎么解决。","content_rendered":"<p>想用 Docker 跑 OpenWrt 做主路由，配置网卡后发现 wlan 网卡被映射成了 eth 网卡，OpenWrt 好像无法通过映射之后的 eth 网卡开热点，请问怎么解决。</p>\n","last_modified":1668221327,"replies":10,"id":894659},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1641783557","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1641783557","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":2992,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1641783557","stars":978,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":360,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":454372,"username":"nothingistrue","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/nothingistrue","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f293fbf9183f02f86b8a61a6c259b1e2?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f293fbf9183f02f86b8a61a6c259b1e2?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f293fbf9183f02f86b8a61a6c259b1e2?s=73&d=retro","created":1574240608,"last_modified":1662346478},"last_reply_by":"nothingistrue","last_touched":1668237331,"title":"实际应用， win11 的重置，还是 OEM 重置，不是干净重装","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894690","created":1668234793,"deleted":0,"content":"电脑：华硕灵耀 X13 。预装不多，就 3 个，但是 2 个毒——迈克菲、WPS 、百度网盘。\r\n\r\n两次重置，一次是设置里面直接重置，一次是高级启动后再 UEFI 重置，都是选择全删除，即删除个人文件、删除驱动器、删除工作区（预装）、云下载。\r\n\r\n回来一看，预装全在。\r\n\r\n目前推测最有可能的原因是：云下载在选择下载来源的时候，选择的华硕的来源，而不是微软的。这里面的门路可能是华硕自己拦截了，也可能是微软给开的后门，具体不得而知，但是这个云下载是铁定不能用了。\r\n\r\n老老实实制作安装 U 盘去了。","content_rendered":"<p>电脑：华硕灵耀 X13 。预装不多，就 3 个，但是 2 个毒——迈克菲、WPS 、百度网盘。</p>\n<p>两次重置，一次是设置里面直接重置，一次是高级启动后再 UEFI 重置，都是选择全删除，即删除个人文件、删除驱动器、删除工作区（预装）、云下载。</p>\n<p>回来一看，预装全在。</p>\n<p>目前推测最有可能的原因是：云下载在选择下载来源的时候，选择的华硕的来源，而不是微软的。这里面的门路可能是华硕自己拦截了，也可能是微软给开的后门，具体不得而知，但是这个云下载是铁定不能用了。</p>\n<p>老老实实制作安装 U 盘去了。</p>\n","last_modified":1668234793,"replies":9,"id":894690},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":192844,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3613,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":597049,"username":"Hellostack","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Hellostack","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0bcc8d1b3addf1cc6e84f3191189bb52?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0bcc8d1b3addf1cc6e84f3191189bb52?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0bcc8d1b3addf1cc6e84f3191189bb52?s=73&d=retro","created":1665475481,"last_modified":1665475481},"last_reply_by":"cmdOptionKana","last_touched":1668238880,"title":"大佬们 编程真的就像搭乐高 盖房子吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894695","created":1668236507,"deleted":0,"content":"这个帖子的大佬说 编程就像搭乐高 盖房子 感觉挺简单的呀 真的就像搭乐高 盖房子吗\r\n\r\nhttps://www.v2ex.com/t/893058?p=2\r\n\r\n为什么编程对我就像母语？\r\n\r\n对我来说编程就是一个娱乐活动，初期类似于在红白机上打坦克，后来像搭乐高，再后来像盖房。一直觉得编程语言这么符合逻辑，就像在说一种自己本来就会的母语。\r\n\r\n其实我学人类语言也是如此，看到语法书就感觉这语法这么有逻辑，感觉我自己也可以写一本语法书。\r\n\r\n请问我为什么会有这种感觉？是普遍现象么？一般人学习编程和学习语言障碍在哪里？","content_rendered":"<p>这个帖子的大佬说 编程就像搭乐高 盖房子 感觉挺简单的呀 真的就像搭乐高 盖房子吗</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/893058?p=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/893058?p=2</a></p>\n<p>为什么编程对我就像母语？</p>\n<p>对我来说编程就是一个娱乐活动，初期类似于在红白机上打坦克，后来像搭乐高，再后来像盖房。一直觉得编程语言这么符合逻辑，就像在说一种自己本来就会的母语。</p>\n<p>其实我学人类语言也是如此，看到语法书就感觉这语法这么有逻辑，感觉我自己也可以写一本语法书。</p>\n<p>请问我为什么会有这种感觉？是普遍现象么？一般人学习编程和学习语言障碍在哪里？</p>\n","last_modified":1668236507,"replies":8,"id":894695},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","ava